name: Blessed Naoto Shirogane Lora
description:
Training models is completely free and costs me absolutely nothing. You can support me by writing me positive reviews. :P

This is the sixth version of the model, I put a lot of work into this for a week until it was good. Trained with the extra legal version of stable diffusion.
Tags:
Character tag - Naoto Shirogane (P4)
Signature hat - cabbie hat
Dancing night outfit - naotodancing
Yasogami school uniform - naotostudent
Detective uniform - naotodetective
Reverse trap - androgynous

The outfits need some extra tagging and a bit of luck to get them to be consistent, the yasogami uniform doesnt work very well sadly. Sub tags id recommend for the outfit tags:
naotodancing - blue shirt, suspenders, yellow necktie, black pants, fingerless gloves,
naotostudent - school uniform, black pants, white collared shirt, black jacket,
naotodetective - detective uniform, blue coat, white trimmed coat, plaid pants,
androgynous - Negative tag: (breasts)

She has two canon eye colors, grey and blue. You can tag which you want. As she's a reverse trap if you dont use the 1girl tag it might draw her as a male with abs. Used a pose/concept lora in 2 of the preview images. Check preview tags for outfit tag examples, nsfw at the end. ((nude)) recommended for full nudity as her outfits will likely pop up
